775
00:47:54,744 --> 00:47:55,826
of a program.

776
00:47:55,826 --> 00:47:57,348
And then those can start

777
00:47:57,348 --> 00:48:00,072
communicating with each other so

778
00:48:00,072 --> 00:48:02,737
that you can implement things like,

779
00:48:02,737 --> 00:48:04,740
divide a large simulation

